 Actzo [VRA1] TYPINI, GNRFRC, VALSTD, TYPVAL, TIMCOD, FORVAR, TIMCMT, CMTDET
Endif
 Actzo [VRA2] FLGEMP, PAGEMP, ROWEMP, PRNFLG1, PRNFLG2, PRNFLG3
 If GTPS
  Actzo [VRA1] TIMVAR, TYPMAJ, DAYTYP, NATCOD
